# BOSS's own dev workspace — root-anchored (leading slash) so the SHIPPED product
# templates under stages/*/template/.claude/ and their CLAUDE.md stay public.
/CLAUDE.md                  # BOSS's own working rules (the founder's dev process)
/.claude/                   # BOSS's own dev agents (mentors, personas), skills, settings
/.boss/                     # BOSS's own machine state (manifest, config)
/BlueprintOS.code-workspace # personal editor config
